	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Mar 16th 11:30 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>From the orc camps to ice goblins, i have tried to get tanks to fight a coordinated battle, from teaching them the /assist key to not hitting the ones that just glowed pink and aren't hitting you.&nbsp;&nbsp;Is there a class we can make tanks take before they are allowed in groups???  I will have an entire camped mezzed than they will go out and attack each individual npc 1 on 1, ignoring everything i am trying to say, and usually killing most of themselves then its my fault for poor crows control....<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
